strings.Value: "I can't stop thinking about the face of that poor woman we found in the cyclops' tomb. A 'Defaced' Sister indeed! Who could have done that to her?"
"A perverse religious practice of some fanatic cult. Priests of many dark religions self-mutilate voluntarily."
"It doesn't matter much now, anyway. You don't need a face to lay in a grave."
"The world is full of such terrors. Life is cruel. What is more surprising is the way you cling to it."
"For some reason I feel they really are sisters... From a very unhappy family."
